Title:          XBomb - X Windows strategy game.
Version:        2.2a [29-Nov-09]
Entered-date:   29NOV09
Description:    A 'minesweeper' style strategy game for UNIX and
                X-Windows. A test of speed and logic to find the
                location of bombs hidden in a grid. A choice of
                hexagonal, square or triangular grids, each in 3
                difficulty levels, all games played against the
                clock, with a high-score table for each.
